What are bed bugs?

Bed bugs are small insects (about the size of an apple seed) with oval-shaped bodies and no wings. They usually come out and bite at night. It is possible for anyone, anywhere to experience a bed bug infestation, but they can be prevented and controlled.

How do I find a pest control company?

Getting rid of bed bugs requires pesticides and other treatments that should only be used by professionals. There are many licensed pest control companies in Ontario who have the training and experience to manage a bed bug infestation.
